	* clamav/vscan-clamav_core.c: make the usage of safe_strcpy/cat() a
	  bit clearer...  last parameter should be sizeof(first_param)-1;
	  like pstrcpy(x,y) -> safe_strcpy(x,y,sizeof(pstring)-1)
